('4259c38f-3e85-4225-82f0-86f0d236ed92', 'About us !', 'about-us', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Welcome to Look Me Cosmetic, where beauty meets innovation. We take pride in being a leading cosmetics company dedicated to providing high-quality products designed to enhance your natural beauty. Our extensive range of skincare and haircare solutions is crafted to empower individuals, helping them look and feel their best.</span></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br></span></b></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Key Features:</span></b><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><b>1. Premium Quality:\r\n</b></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> At Look Me Cosmetic, we are committed to delivering excellence. Our products are meticulously formulated using top-grade ingredients, ensuring superior quality and effectiveness.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><b>2. Innovation:\r\n</b>We are always at the forefront of the industry, embracing innovation to meet the evolving needs of our customers. Our dedicated research and development team works tirelessly to create cutting-edge formulas that set new standards in beauty care.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><b>3. Diverse Product Range:\r\n</b>Look Me Cosmetic offers a comprehensive range of products to cater to all your beauty needs. From luxurious glycerin to nourishing treatment creams and revitalizing hair serums, we have carefully curated our collection. Whether you seek to hydrate your skin, address specific concerns, or enhance the health and shine of your hair, Look Me Cosmetic has you covered.</span><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Discover the perfect blend of science and beauty at Look Me Cosmetic, where every product is a testament to our commitment to your radiant and confident self.</span><br></p>', 0, 1, 1, 1, '2024-01-03 03:22:13', '2024-01-03 07:27:55'),
('45eccebe-fe2c-454a-9d00-23e51783daaf', 'Return Policy', 'return-policy', '<p><b>Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. - Product Return Policy</b></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Thank you for choosing Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. for your beauty and skincare needs. Our commitment is to provide you with high-quality products and excellent customer service. In the event that you need to return a product, please review our return policy guidelines below:</span><br></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">1. Eligibility for Returns:</b><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Products must be returned within 30 days of the purchase date.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- The product must be in its original packaging, unused, and in the same condition as received.</p><p><br></p><p><b>2. Non-Returnable Items:</b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Certain products, such as opened or used cosmetics, are not eligible for return due to hygiene reasons.</p><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">3. Return Process:</span><br></b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- To initiate a return, please contact our customer service team at [sales@lookmecosmetic.com] or call [Call Office: 025586765] to obtain a Return Authorization Number (RAN).</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Clearly mark the RAN on the outside of the package.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Ship the product, along with a copy of the original invoice and a brief explanation of the reason for the return, to our Corporate Address in Itahari, Sunsari, Nepal.</p><p><br></p><p><b>4. Return Shipping:</b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Customers are responsible for the cost of return shipping, unless the return is due to an error on our part.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- We recommend using a trackable shipping method to ensure that the return is received.</p><p><br></p><p><b>5. Refund or Exchange:</b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Once the returned product is received and inspected, we will process either a refund or exchange, based on your preference.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;- Refunds will be issued to the original payment method.</p><p><br></