('16884fcf-4be8-43d4-b1c7-a53586d4365d', 'Hair Serum', 'hair-serum', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e6bf00b7-7fff-856e-9bd0-9711a850db49\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Look Me High Gloss Hair Serum contains a blend of chemical and mineral blockers, enriched with skin-friendly ingredients like niacinamide, ferulic acid, colloidal oatmeal, Kakadu plum, tea tree, and hyaluronic acid. Infused with vitamin E, this budget-friendly serum provides essential elements for soft, smooth hair.</span></p>', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e6bf00b7-7fff-856e-9bd0-9711a850db49\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font color=\"#374151\">Transform your tresses with a touch of magic – let the hair serum spell begin.</font></span><br></p>', '<p>Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. - Product Return Policy</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Thank you for choosing Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. for your beauty and skincare needs. Our commitment is to provide you with high-quality products and excellent customer service. In the event that you need to return a product, please review our return policy guidelines in link Below&nbsp;<br></span><a href=\"https://lookmecosmetic.com/page/return-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Return Policy</a><br></p>', 'ml', 1, 1.00, NULL, 'f33820f5-b54b-4645-9ea6-6ffdb86296b9', NULL, 'No', '1500', '123456', 'Yes', 1248, 1, '2024-01-01 07:28:51', '2024-01-22 10:14:40'),
('3ace17ee-d52b-40f1-8516-8ec3b68a4045', 'Pure Glycerin', 'pure-glycerin', '<h3 class=\"\"><b>Glycerine and Skin Health: Unveiling the Benefits</b></h3><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Glycerine is Skin care product to protect your skin from\r\ncrack, keep smooth sand moisture. Here are some Benefits</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Hydration and Moisture Retention:</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Glycerine is a powerful humectant, meaning it attracts and\r\nretains moisture from the air. This property makes it an excellent ingredient\r\nfor hydrating the skin. When applied topically, glycerine helps to draw and\r\nlock in moisture, preventing skin dehydration.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Softening and Smoothing</b> <br>\r\nWhen applied to the skin, glycerine imparts a soft and smooth texture. It helps\r\nto make the skin feel supple by preventing dryness and roughness. This quality\r\nmakes glycerine a common ingredient in moisturizers and lotions.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Compatibility with All Skin Types <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Glycerine is suitable for all skin types, including\r\nsensitive and acne-prone skin. Its non-comedogenic nature means it doesn\'t clog\r\npores, making it a versatile choice for a wide range of skincare products.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Anti-Aging Properties <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Proper skin hydration is crucial for maintaining its\r\nelasticity and preventing premature aging. Glycerine aids in reducing the\r\nappearance of fine lines and wrinkles by keeping the skin well-moisturized and\r\npromoting a youthful complexion.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Wound Healing and Scar Reduction <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Glycerine\'s moisturizing and skin-protective properties\r\ncontribute to the healing process of wounds and can minimize the formation of\r\nscars. It helps create an optimal environment for the skin to repair itself.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Versatility in Formulations <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Skincare products, such as cleansers, toners, serums, and\r\nmasks, often contain glycerine due to its versatility. It can be seamlessly\r\nincorporated into various formulations to address specific skincare needs.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Affordability and Availability <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Glycerine is a cost-effective and widely available\r\ningredient, making it accessible for a broad range of consumers. Its\r\naffordability ensures that high-quality skincare products with glycerine can be\r\nfound across different price points.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">In summary, glycerine stands out as a versatile and\r\nbeneficial ingredient in skincare, providing a multitude of advantages that\r\ncontribute to the overall health and appearance of the skin. Whether used alone\r\nor in combination with other ingredients, glycerine remains a staple in the\r\nworld of skincare.<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Maya Me Pure Glycine, For Soft and Shining Skin&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '<p>....</p>', 'ml', 100, 0.50, NULL, 'b7e97894-893e-42a8-924b-3741760e5de0', NULL, 'No', '1675', NULL, 'Yes', 500, 1, '2024-01-03 07:24:11', '2024-01-22 10:07:47'),
('645e02df-0e93-4acb-973f-41416e3b8f16', 'Bleaching Power', 'bleaching-power', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">What is Blonde Powder?</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Blondor Multi Blonde Powder by Look Me is a fast and easy-to-mix lightening powder. It produces a creamier consistency for a professional application and is a favorite among hairdressers. This best-seller within the Blondor range is designed for controlled and reliable lightening, offering up to 7 levels of lift. It is suitable for all lightening techniques.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">How Do You Mix Blonde Powder and Developer?</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-655159c7-7fff-7b0c-78f7-5b4a0f4138c9\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Follow this rule of thumb while mixing Look Me Blonde Powder and developer: Always add one part bleach with 2 parts of the developer. Alternatively, use 4 ounces of the developer with 2 ounces of bleach. This rule applies even if you use 40 volumes of developers. Ensure thorough mixing for consistent and effective results in your hair lightening process.</span></p>', '<p><br></p><p>Illuminate Your Beauty: Unleash the Radiance with Our Premium Bleach Powder!<br></p>', '<p>Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. - Product Return Policy</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Thank you for choosing Look Me Cosmetic Pvt. Ltd. for your beauty and skincare needs. Our commitment is to provide you with high-quality products and excellent customer service. In the event that you need to return a product, please review our return policy guidelines in link Below&nbsp;<br></span><a href=\"https://lookmecosmetic.com/page/return-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Return Policy</a></p>', 'ml', 250, 650.00, NULL, 'f33820f5-b54b-4645-9ea6-6ffdb86296b9', NULL, 'No', '15000', '15522', 'Yes', 5722, 1, '2024-01-03 03:59:15', '2024-01-15 15:07:50'),
('a71c8994-de52-4d9b-8143-023f4396e040', 'HAIR STRAIGHT CREAM', 'hair-straight-cream', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Transform your hair into sleek, silky strands with our Hair Elegance Straightening Cream, an advanced hair rebonding lotion commonly utilized in top salons. Our formula is meticulously crafted with precision, blending ingredients like sodium hydroxide or guanidine hydroxide, sulfites for an ammoniacal mixture, and thiol compounds, including nourishing ammonium keratin infused with aloe vera.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">How to Use Look Me Hair Elegance Straightening Cream:</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-dcd2bd60-7fff-42c6-0a5f-acf2c58adbc2\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:none;font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:15pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#374151;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Preparation:</span></p></li><ul style=\"marg